text: The 2015–16 Utah State Aggies women's basketball team represents Utah State University in the 2015–16 college basketball season. The Aggies, led by fourth year head coach Jerry Finkbeiner. The Aggies played their home games at the Smith Spectrum and were third year members of the Mountain West Conference. They finished the season 14–17, 8–10 in Mountain West play to finish in seventh place.
